These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, disaster, musical, family
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person watching sports movies is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | family | musical | disaster | sports   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, thriller, family, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | family | action | thriller | comedy    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, funk, classical
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the fan of dubstep is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep | classical | funk   | disco |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, purple, lilac, amber
1. the person who likes purple is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Color         | purple | amber   | lilac | pink |

