.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, folk, disco
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre    | reggae       | disco | folk | punk     |

