.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, pomegranate, papaya, avocado
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | avocado | papaya | radish | pomegranate |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

