2. the fan of rock is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
