.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, ebony, coral
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | yellow    | ebony       | brown | coral   |
| Transport     | helicopter | motorbike | ship   | airplane |

