2. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | grapes | lettuce | cranberry | orange  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish      | frog | ferret |

