.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, lily, amaryllis
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the person who growsrose##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growslily is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Flower   | lily | tulip  | rose | amaryllis   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

